      "author_association": "MEMBER",
      "body": "Hello Rovikin,\r\n\r\nThe BIP 39 authors no longer accepts additional word lists, they generally restrict themselves to focus only on an English wordlist. I am afraid that I do not know where your wordlist should be submitted eventually, since neither BIP39 nor the WLIPs seem to be looking to incorporate further lists. Perhaps this would be a topic to discuss with other Indonesian Bitcoin users.\r\n\r\nFor example you could consider writing a separate BIP instead or to publish your wordlist independently.",
